(b) Allow the user to specify the start and end to the table (e.g., 4 to 15)
(c) Allow the user to specify the step size (e.g., by 3 is 4, 7, 10, 13).*/

class countLoopsEx2
{
  public static void main(String[] args)
  {
    int mult, ans, start, end;
    
    System.out.println("1-12 x table");
    System.out.println("What number to multiply: ");
    mult = In.getInt();
    
    System.out.println("When to start ");
    start = In.getInt();
    
    System.out.println("When to end: ");
    end = In.getInt();
    
    for(int i = start; i <=end; i++)
    {
      ans = i*mult;
      System.out.println(mult + " x " + i + " is equal to: " + ans);
    }
    
  }
}